    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1944-11-29T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-11-29T00:00:00-05:00" n="87"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d87">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.34553B/11–2944</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum by the <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss> to President <persName type="to">Roosevelt</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-11-29">November 29,
                            1944</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The final agreement<note n="32" xml:id="d87fn1">For text of exchange of notes,
                        agreement, and supplementary exchange of notes signed at Lisbon, November
                        28, 1944. see Department of State, Treaties and Other International Acts
                        Series No. 2338, or 2 UST (pt. 2) 2124.</note> for the additional air base
                    in Santa Maria, Azores, was signed yesterday and the Portuguese Government has
                    instructed the Azores authorities to turn the base over to the United States
                    Army for immediate use.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>E. R. <hi rend="smallcaps">Stettinius, Jr.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
